			<header class="entry-header">

				<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="name">Manuel Valls intensifie la lutte contre le cyberterrorisme</h1>

				<div class="entry-author-date">
					<span class="author vcard">Ariane Beky</span>, <span class="date"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2015-01-21T15:39:11+01:00" itemprop="datePublished">21 janvier 2015, 15:39</time></span>				</div>
								<div itemprop="breadcrumb" class="entry-breadcrumb"><a href="https://www.silicon.fr/actualites/security/cyberwar" title="View all posts in Cyberguerre">Cyberguerre</a><a href="https://www.silicon.fr/actualites/e-regulation/legal" title="View all posts in Legislation">Legislation</a><a href="https://www.silicon.fr/actualites/e-regulation" title="View all posts in Régulations">Régulations</a><a href="https://www.silicon.fr/actualites/security" title="View all posts in Sécurité">Sécurité</a></div>				<div class="entry-tools"></div>

			</header>
			<!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="articleWrapper">
												<div class="entry-social-v3 postID-106359" data-postid="106359">
